<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>M5-ticket Find Book Travel</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --indigo: #0022d2;
        --indigo-tint: #ebedff;
        --black: #0a0a0a;
        --grey-700: #3a3a3a;
        --grey-500: #6b6b6b;
        --grey-300: #c4c4c4;
        --grey-100: #f2f2f2;
        --white: #ffffff;
        --red: #fb8c00;
        --red-tint: #fff3e0;
        --red-text: #b35900;
        --radius-sm: 8px;
        --radius-md: 12px;
        --radius-lg: 18px;
        --radius-pill: 999px;
        --shadow-card: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        --font: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
        --transition: 0.18s ease;
      }
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      html {
        font-family: var(--font);
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      body {
        background: var(--grey-100);
        color: var(--black);
        min-height: 100dvh;
      }
      button {
        cursor: pointer;
        border: none;
        background: none;
        font-family: inherit;
      }
      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .header {
        background: var(--white);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 100;
      }
      .header-inner {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 16px;
        height: 56px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 40px;
      }
      .logo {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }
      .logo-icon {
        width: 34px;
        height: 34px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
        background: var(--indigo);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .logo-icon svg {
        width: 18px;
        height: 18px;
        fill: var(--white);
      }
      .logo-name {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--indigo);
        letter-spacing: -0.4px;
      }
      .logo-tag {
        font-size: 9px;
        color: var(--grey-500);
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }
      .hero {
        background: var(--red);
        padding: 28px 16px 72px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--white);
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      .hero-title span {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-weight: 400;
      }
      .hero-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        padding: 5px 14px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--white);
      }
      .result-wrap {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: -48px auto 0;
        padding: 0 16px 80px;
      }
      .btn-back {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--indigo);
        background: var(--indigo-tint);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 34, 210, 0.15);
        padding: 9px 18px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        transition: var(--transition);
      }
      .btn-back:hover {
        background: var(--indigo);
        color: var(--white);
      }

      /* failure card */
      .failure-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1.5px solid rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.15);
        animation: slideUp 0.25s ease both;
      }
      @keyframes slideUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(12px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }
      .failure-head {
        background: var(--red-tint);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.15);
        padding: 20px 18px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .failure-icon {
        font-size: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .failure-title {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--red-text);
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .failure-sub {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--grey-500);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      /* search summary */
      .search-summary {
        padding: 18px 18px 0;
      }
      .search-summary-title {
        font-size: 10px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--grey-500);
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .search-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-100);
        gap: 10px;
      }
      .search-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .search-key {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--grey-500);
        font-weight: 500;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .search-val-wrap {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        min-width: 0;
      }
      .search-val {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--black);
        text-align: right;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      .search-row.is-bad .search-val {
        color: var(--red-text);
      }
      .field-flag {
        font-size: 9px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        padding: 2px 7px;
        border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
        flex-shrink: 0;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
      .field-flag.bad {
        background: var(--red-tint);
        color: var(--red-text);
        border: 1px solid rgba(244, 67, 54, 0.25);
      }

      /* try again button */
      .failure-footer {
        padding: 18px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--grey-100);
      }
      .btn-try-again {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 14px;
        background: var(--indigo);
        color: var(--white);
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 34, 210, 0.35);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 8px;
        transition: var(--transition);
      }
      .btn-try-again svg {
        width: 18px;
        height: 18px;
        fill: var(--white);
      }
      .btn-try-again:hover {
        background: #0019a8;
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .footer-nav {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        background: var(--white);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        display: flex;
        z-index: 100;
      }
      @media (min-width: 640px) {
        .footer-nav {
          display: none;
        }
      }
      @media (max-width: 639px) {
        body {
          padding-bottom: 64px;
        }
      }

      .help-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }
      .help-card-head {
        padding: 14px 18px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-100);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3px;
      }
      .help-card-title {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--black);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 7px;
      }
      .help-card-sub {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--grey-500);
      }

      .help-section-label {
        font-size: 10px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--grey-500);
        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 14px 18px 8px;
      }

      .tip-row {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 10px 18px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey-100);
      }
      .tip-row:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .tip-icon-wrap {
        font-size: 18px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 1px;
        color: var(--grey-500);
      }
      .tip-title {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--black);
        margin-bottom: 3px;
      }
      .tip-desc {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--grey-500);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="header-inner">
        <div class="logo">
          <div class="logo-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M4 4h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2zm0 2v8h16V6H4zm-1 10l-1 3h20l-1-3H3zm5 1h8v1H8v-1zM6 9h12v2H6V9zm0-2h12v1H6V7z"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="logo-name">M5-ticket</div>
            <div class="logo-tag">Find - Book - Travel</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Search Couldn't Run<br /><span>Check your input below</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="hero-badge">⚠️ INVALID INPUT — Please correct &amp; retry</div>
    </section>

    <div class="result-wrap">
      <a href="/" class="btn-back">
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          style="width: 14px; height: 14px; fill: currentColor"
        >
          <path
            d="M20 11H7.83l5.59-5.59L12 4l-8 8 8 8 1.41-1.41L7.83 13H20v-2z"
          />
        </svg>
        Search Again
      </a>

      <!-- failure card -->
      <div class="failure-card">
        <div class="failure-head">
          <div class="failure-icon">⚠️</div>
          <div class="failure-title">We Couldn't Process Your Search</div>
          <div class="failure-sub">
            One or more of the values you entered doesn't look right. Please
            review the fields below and try again.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- search summary: values as entered -->
        <div class="search-summary">
          <div class="search-summary-title">What You Entered</div>

          <div class="search-row">
            <span class="search-key">Train No.</span>
            <div class="search-val-wrap">
              <span class="search-val"><%= trainNo %></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="search-row">
            <span class="search-key">From Station</span>
            <div class="search-val-wrap">
              <span class="search-val"><%= fromStnCode %></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="search-row">
            <span class="search-key">To Station</span>
            <div class="search-val-wrap">
              <span class="search-val"><%= toStnCode %></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="search-row">
            <span class="search-key">Date</span>
            <div class="search-val-wrap">
              <span class="search-val"><%= date %></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="search-row">
            <span class="search-key">Coach</span>
            <div class="search-val-wrap">
              <span class="search-val"><%= coach %></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="search-row">
            <span class="search-key">Quota</span>
            <div class="search-val-wrap">
              <span class="search-val"><%= quota %></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- try again -->
        <div class="failure-footer">
          <a href="/" class="btn-try-again">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M17.65 6.35A7.958 7.958 0 0 0 12 4c-4.42 0-7.99 3.58-7.99 8s3.57 8 7.99 8c3.73 0 6.84-2.55 7.73-6h-2.08A5.99 5.99 0 0 1 12 18c-3.31 0-6-2.69-6-6s2.69-6 6-6c1.66 0 3.14.69 4.22 1.78L13 11h7V4l-2.35 2.35z"
              />
            </svg>
            Correct &amp; Search Again
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- static tips: common input mistakes -->
      <div class="help-card">
        <div class="help-card-head">
          <div class="help-card-title">📋 Common Input Mistakes</div>
          <div class="help-card-sub">
            Double-check these before searching again
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-row">
          <div class="tip-icon-wrap">🚆</div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <div class="tip-title">Train number must be 5 digits</div>
            <div class="tip-desc">
              Make sure you entered the full numeric train number with no
              letters or extra spaces, e.g. 12345.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-row">
          <div class="tip-icon-wrap">🗺️</div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <div class="tip-title">Station codes must be valid IRCTC codes</div>
            <div class="tip-desc">
              Use the official station abbreviation (e.g. NDLS, BCT), not the
              full city name.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-row">
          <div class="tip-icon-wrap">🔁</div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <div class="tip-title">From and To stations can't be the same</div>
            <div class="tip-desc">
              Check that your source and destination stations are different
              and are actually on this train's route.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-row">
          <div class="tip-icon-wrap">📅</div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <div class="tip-title">Date must be today or a future date</div>
            <div class="tip-desc">
              Use the format shown in the search box, and make sure it isn't a
              date in the past.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-row">
          <div class="tip-icon-wrap">💺</div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <div class="tip-title">Coach class must match a valid class code</div>
            <div class="tip-desc">
              Common values are SL, 3A, 2A, 1A, CC, 2S — check there's no typo.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-row">
          <div class="tip-icon-wrap">🎟️</div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <div class="tip-title">Quota must be a supported option</div>
            <div class="tip-desc">
              Use GN (General), TQ (Tatkal), PT (Premium Tatkal), or LD
              (Ladies) — other values won't be recognized.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="footer-nav"></nav>
  </body>
</html>
